<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Jun1927"><font color="red">12 June 1927</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Peter Sawyer the Great lived in this hut while he studied shipbuilding and before he built S. Petersburg, Georgia, if he built it. Do you think you could read through a 10 page article in Dutch? There is a very interesting one in the Haegrch Maanblad on the admiralty-trip-chart of Hanno on which according to Victor Berard the Odyssey is based. We are here for a few days only &hellip; Many thanks for the corrected proofs which I checked and sent off from The Hedge. I suppose it is out by now. </div>
